Insurgo.text: Hearing of the case will be concluded this week

Intectus.text: Hearing of the case will last for several days

Macies.text: Judge has concluded his summing-up. It was in favour of defendant

Mactator.text: Judge has concluded his summing-up. It was in favour of neither party

Madefeci.text: Judge has concluded his summing-up. It was in favour of plaintiff

Magnus.text: Jury could not agree, and have been discharged

Majestas.text: Subpoena as a witness on our side

Maledice.text: Subpœna has not been served, as we cannot find ---

Maligne.text: Summons has been issued, returnable on ---

Manceps.text: Summons heard to-day. Adjourned for a week

Manedum.text: Summons heard to-day. Adjourned into court

Manifeste.text: Summons heard to-day. Chief clerk reserves decision

Manliana.text: Summons heard to-day. Master reserves decision

Mansito.text: Summons heard to-day. Order made as asked

Marceo.text: Summons heard to-day. Order refused, with costs
